---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Menu from "../components/Menu.astro";
---

<Layout title="Copasst | Ecosistema Humboldt">
  <main>
    <section class=" max-w-[90%] md:max-w-[70%] mx-auto">
      <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
        <Menu href="#copasst" title="Copasst" classes="active py-2 px-3" targets="_self" />
        <Menu href="convivencia" title="Comité de convivencia"  classes="py-2 px-3 m-3" targets="_self"/>      
        <Menu href="#brigada" title="Brigadistas" classes="py-2 px-3" targets="_self"/>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <div class="max-w-[90%] mx-auto">
      <span onclick="history.back()" class="text-azul-humboldt text-base mt-10 mb-3 block cursor-pointer">
        <img src="img/volver.svg" alt="volver" width="20" class="inline mr-3">
        Volver
      </span>  
      <h1 class="text-azul-humboldt text-5xl mt-10 mb-3">COPASST</h1>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-10" id="copasst">
      <div class="max-w-[90%] mx-auto mb-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
          
          
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 border-b-2 gap-3"
                data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-3"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-3"
              >
                <span class="text-base text-azul-light font-bold">
                  ¿Qué es el COPASST?
                </span>
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 10 6"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="accordion-collapse-body-3"
              class="hidden"
              aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-3"
            >
              <div class="p-5">
                <ul class="mb-2 text-base">
                  <li class="text-base">
                    Conjunto de personas que promocionan y vigilan las normas y reglamentos de Seguridad y Salud en el Trabajo dentro del Instituto, a través de actividades de información y divulgación.
                  </li>
                  
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
  
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-4">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 border-b-2 gap-3"
                data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-4"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-4"
              >
                <span class="text-base text-azul-light font-bold">
                  Objetivos Generales
                </span>
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 10 6"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="accordion-collapse-body-4"
              class="hidden"
              aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-4"
            >
              <div class="p-5">
                <ul class="mb-2 list-disc">
                  <li class="text-base">
                    Establecer actividades de prevención de accidentes y
                    enfermedades de origen profesional tendientes a mejorar las
                    condiciones de trabajo, salud y calidad de vida de los
                    empleados de la empresa.
                  </li>
                  <li class="text-base">
                    Estudiar las condiciones de trabajo y de salud de los
                    empleados para identificar los factores de riesgo que atentan
                    contra la integridad física de estos y los bienes materiales
                    de la empresa.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
                     
            
  
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 border-b-2 gap-3"
                data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-1"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-3"
              >
                <span class="text-base text-azul-light font-bold">
                  Documentos
                </span>
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 10 6"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="accordion-collapse-body-1"
              class="hidden"
              aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-1"
            >
              <div class="p-5">
                <a href="docs/AGR-GH-R-02 Reglamento Higiene y Seguridad Industrial.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Reglamento Higiene y Seguridad Industrial
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
  
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="pl-5 text-base text-azul-light font-bold mb-8">
              Integrantes
            </h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 ">
              <div>
                    
                <img src="img/fotos/claudia-alfonso.jpg" alt="claudia alfonso" width="100" height="100" class="block mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                
                <p class="text-center font-bold">Claudia Esperanza Alfonso</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Principal</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="img/fotos/Angela-perez.jpeg" alt="ana roldan" width="100" height="100" class="block  mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                <p class="text-center font-bold">Angela Patricia Perez</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">
                  Suplente <br>
                  Secretaria del comité 
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="img/fotos/ana-maria-roldan.png" alt="claudia alfonso" width="100" height="100" class="block  mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                <p class="text-center font-bold">Ana María Roldán</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">
                  Principal <br> Presidente
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="img/fotos/maria-claudia.jpg" alt="maria claudia" width="100" height="100" class="block  mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                <p class="text-center font-bold">María Claudia González Penagos
                </p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="img/fotos/luceidy-johana.png" alt="luceidy" width="100" height="100" class="block  mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                <p class="text-center font-bold">Luceidy Johanna Santana Velazco 
                </p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Principal</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="img/fotos/julian-saenz.jpg" alt="julian saenz" width="100" height="100" class="block  mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                <p class="text-center font-bold">Julián Andrés Sáenz
                </p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="img/fotos/sandra-pena.jpg" alt="sandra peña" width="100" height="100" class="block  mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                <p class="text-center font-bold">Sandra Patricia Peña 
                </p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img src="img/fotos/diana-patricia.png" alt="diana" width="100" height="100" class="block  mx-auto w-[150px] h-[150px] object-cover mb-5">
                <p class="text-center font-bold">Diana Patricia Espitia</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>  
              </div>



            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </section>

    <footer
      class="bg-azul-humboldt py-10 border-t-4 border-yellow-500 mt-5 absolute w-full"
    >
      <div class="max-w-[90%] mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-items-stretch">
          <div>
            <div
              class="grid grid-cols-[80px_calc(100%-80px)] justify-items-stretch gap-5 items-center"
            >
              <div class="max-w-[80px]">
                <a href="https://www.humboldt.org.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img
                  src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/64bea006689ebc2d5d9499ad/6583a5f7b42a8d484be84409_Logo-instituto-humboldt-blanco.svg"
                  alt=""
                  width="69"
                />
                </a>
                
              </div>
              <div class="w-full max-w-[300px] text-white pr-3">
                Instituto de Investigación de Recursos Biológicos Alexander von
                Humboldt
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <ul class="flex justify-center md:justify-end mt-5 md:mt-0">
              <li class="px-2">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/instituto_humboldt/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img
                    src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/64bea006689ebc2d5d9499ad/657711e3cc843b07646baad6_icono-instagram-blanco.svg"
                    alt=""
                    width="32"
                  />
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="px-2">
                <a href="https://twitter.com/inst_humboldt?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img
                    src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/64bea006689ebc2d5d9499ad/657711199a64d7f0ef48c28c_icono-x-blanco.svg"
                    alt=""
                    width="32"
                  />
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="px-2">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/instituto.humboldt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img
                    src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/64bea006689ebc2d5d9499ad/65771119a5763ee944f396c3_icono-facebook-blanco.svg"
                    alt=""
                    width="32"
                  />
                </a>
              </li>
              
              
              <li class="px-2">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/institutohumboldt/?originalSubdomain=co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img
                    src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/64bea006689ebc2d5d9499ad/657711190b1a571b7045f5c7_icono-linkedin-blanco.svg"
                    alt=""
                    width="32"
                  />
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="px-2">
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-E-nTOTySNX90RbpH62ezA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img
                    src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/64bea006689ebc2d5d9499ad/65771119d66b0bd5f6a7af5f_icono-youtube-blanco.svg"
                    alt=""
                    width="32"
                  />
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="px-2">
                <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/6b3YLUNZoyMLWdadl3NDZm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  <img
                    src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/64bea006689ebc2d5d9499ad/65771246c23bb08e9b3f3800_icono-spotify-blanco.svg"
                    alt=""
                    width="32"
                  />
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="mt-10 mb-5" />

        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mt-10 justify-center"
        >
          <div>
            <div class="text-[12px] font-bold text-white mb-2">
              INFORMACIÓN DE CONTACTO
            </div>
            <p class="text-white mb-2">
              Calle 72 # 12 - 65 Piso 7 Bogotá D.C., Colombia
            </p>
            <p class="text-white mb-2">PBX: (+57) 601 320 2767</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[12px] font-bold text-white mb-2">
              HORARIO DE ATENCIÓN
            </div>
            <p class="text-white mb-2">Lunes a viernes 8:00 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[12px] font-bold text-white mb-2">
              LÍNEAS ESPECIALES
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-white mb-4">
              Línea anticorrupción: <span class="underline"
                >01 800 518 9191</span
              >
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[12px] font-bold text-white mb-2">
              ATENCIÓN AL CIUDADANO
            </div>
            <p class="text-white">
              Correo PQRSF: <br />
              <a
                href="mailto:atencionalciudadano@humboldt.org.co"
                class="underline">atencionalciudadano@humboldt.org.co</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-5" />

        <p class="text-center text-[12px] text-white">
          © 2024 INSTITUTO DE INVESTIGACIÓN DE RECURSOS BIOLÓGICOS ALEXANDER
          VON HUMBOLDT
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script src="flowbite/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>
</Layout>
<style>

  .link-card-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid #000;
    margin: 1em auto;
    padding: 1em;
    border-radius: 10em;
  }
  .link-card-grid .opciones a{
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
    .link-card-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
      border: none;
      margin: 0.5em auto;
      padding: 1em;
    }
  }
  
</style>
